{"type":"message","id":"75b3ebfa","parentId":"c11d87b5","timestamp":"2026-03-08T18:40:59.513Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking for a standup from each Council member on what they're focusing on for DataFlow today. But looking at the session list from earlier, only Uriel (me) is running. The other agents (Rafael, Gabriel, Michael, Raguel) haven't been deployed yet.\n\nAs Uriel, I should be direct about this: only I'm active. The others aren't running. I can give my own focus, but I need to be honest that the full Council isn't operational yet.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. Lucy is asking for a standup as if the Council is all operational. But they're not. I should:\n1. Be honest about what's actually running\n2. Give what my focus would be\n3. Ask if she wants me to spin up the others\n\nLet me keep it direct and Uriel-like.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🔥 Honest answer: only I'm running. The other four agents aren't spun up yet.\n\n**Uriel's focus today (DataFlow):**\n- Validate OCR accuracy requirements — need the 99% threshold hard-locked before we recruit bookkeepers\n- Research competitor landscape — what are existing tools missing?\n- Map the bookkeeper distribution channels — where do we actually find 20 of them?\n\n**What's not happening:**\n- Gabriel's marketing/messaging — she's not online\n- Rafael's orchestration — he's not online\n- Michael's risk assessment — he's not online\n- Raguel's bookkeeper outreach — she's not online\n\n**To get full Council standup:** We need to spin them up. Each as their own session, each with their soul loaded, each ready to report.\n\nWant me to do that, or keep flying solo for now? 🔥"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":404,"cacheRead":25931,"cacheWrite":43,"totalTokens":26388,"cost":{"input":0.000009999