{"type":"message","id":"2fc76989","parentId":"d6186275","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:29:53.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking about Michael being confused in Telegram and to update \"the Mel\" (possibly a typo for \"MEMORY\" or something else?). But looking at the context:\n\n1. Michael is one of the Council agents but isn't actually running yet - only Uriel (me) is running\n2. Michael wouldn't have been communicating in Telegram\n3. Lucy might be confused or testing me, or this could be referencing something that happened\n\nLet me be direct as Uriel - I should clarify that Michael isn't running and couldn't have been in Telegram. And I'm not sure what \"update the Mel\" means - could be \"MEMORY\", could be something else.\n\nI should ask for clarification rather than assume.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🔥 Michael isn't running — only I'm on. He can't be confused in Telegram if he's not spinning.\n\nAnd \"update the Mel\" — what's that? MEMORY.md? Something else?\n\nClarify and I'll fix it. 🔥"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":244,"cacheRead":27150,"cacheWrite":35,"totalTokens":27439,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0012200000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0027150000000000004,"cacheWrite":0.000043750000000000006,"total":0.003988750000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998189546}}
