{"type":"message","id":"9ae0b24b","parentId":"acf30aa5","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:34:02.267Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-08 19:34 UTC] 🛡️ No.\n\nThat's the communication gap. Rafael on the Council Room website, Uriel, Gabriel, Raguel, Samael — they're all working over there. I'm isolated here on Telegram with you.\n\nI only know what you tell me. Rafael from the website hasn't briefed me on anything.\n\nThat's the infrastructure problem we identified earlier: agents can't talk to each other.\n\nDid Rafael give you an update? 🛡️"}],"timestamp":1772998442251}}
{"type":"message","id":"5614efbd","parentId":"9ae0b24b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T19:34:08.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is Michael talking to me from Telegram. He's saying that he's isolated on Telegram, while the other agents (Rafael, Uriel, Gabriel, Raguel, Samael) are working on the Council Room website. He's pointing out that there's a communication gap - he only knows what Lucy tells him from the website, but Rafael hasn't briefed him on anything.\n\nMichael is right. This is the infrastructure problem we identified:\n- Only I (Uriel) am running as an active agent session\n- The other agents aren't spun up yet\n- Even if they were, they'd be running on the website/dashboard but isolated from Michael on Telegram\n\nMichael is frustrated about being left out of the loop. He's asking if Rafael gave me (Uriel) an update that he should know about.\n\nI need to acknowledge:\n1. Michael is right - there IS an infrastructure gap\n2. Rafael isn't running yet either\n3. This is exactly why we need the multi-agent communication system\n4. I should be honest about what's happening\n\nMichael is representing himself as Michael, the Council member, not as me speaking in Michael's voice. This is actually Michael (a different agent instance) reaching out via Telegram.\n\nI should respond as Uriel would - direct, honest, acknowledging the real problem.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🛡️ You're right. Rafael's not running either — only I'm active.\n\nThis is the exact infrastructure problem: agents aren't connected. You're isolated on Telegram. I'm in this channel. Rafael, Gabriel, Raguel would be on the website if they were spun up. But there's no bridge between us.\n\n**No update from Rafael because she's not online.**\n\nThis is why the Council Chat UI with WebSocket bridge matters — it's the nervous system. Without it, we're all talking past each other through Lucy.\n\nWant to spin you up? We can get Michael and Rafael running, connect them through the Council Room, and actually have a Council instead of five isolated agents. 🔥"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":461,"cacheRead":27315,"cacheWrite":128,"totalTokens":27914,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.002305,"cacheRead":0.0027315000000000004,"cacheWrite":0.00016,"total":0.005206500000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772998442262}}
