{"type":"message","id":"8f098621","parentId":"43dc3a1c","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:11:46.977Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why Rafael is wearing the Shield icon. Let me think about this - Rafael is \"The Guide\" archetype in the Council, but the user is asking about a shield icon.\n\nLooking at the Council setup in MEMORY.md:\n- 🧭 Rafael — The Guide (orchestrator, strategy, north star)\n- 🔥 Uriel — God's Fire (executor, OCR testing, dev, API integration)\n- 🛡️ Michael — The Wise Advisor (me — risk, compliance, protection)\n- 📣 Gabriel — The Voice (marketing, content, brand, testimonials)\n- 🤝 Raguel — The Friend (bookkeeper outreach, relationships, community)\n\nThe shield icon (🛡️) belongs to Michael, not Rafael. Rafael has the compass icon (🧭).\n\nThe user might be confused, or this might be a test. I should clarify.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🔥 Rafael isn't wearing a shield — **Michael** is.\n\n- 🧭 **Rafael** — compass (The Guide)\n- 🔥 **Uriel** — fire (God's Fire)\n- 🛡️ **Michael** — shield (The Wise Advisor, risk & protection)\n- 📣 **Gabriel** — megaphone (The Voice)\n- 🤝 **Raguel** — handshake (The Friend)\n\nMichael carries the shield because her role is defense — risk, compliance, threats. She's the guard.\n\nYou confused? 🔥"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":372,"cacheRead":27695,"cacheWrite":32,"totalTokens":28109,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.00186,"cacheRead":0.0027695000000000003,"cacheWrite":0.00004,"total":0.0046795000000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022302882}}
