{"type":"message","id":"1a86b9d7","parentId":"87b34a65","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:15:30.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Rafael's directory only has SOUL.md. No IDENTITY.md. Let me update Rafael's SOUL.md to include the emoji at the top, and ensure Michael's has the shield emoji in their SOUL.md files. Let me first check Michael's soul to see if it has an emoji defined.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_eO1I6bkTdboA3ynaqAHThs","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-uriel/souls/michael/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":147,"cacheRead":31569,"cacheWrite":215,"totalTokens":31941,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0007350000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0031569000000000002,"cacheWrite":0.00026875,"total":0.004170650000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773022528267}}
{"type":"message","id":"3548f043","parentId":"1a86b9d7","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:15:30.510Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tooluse_eO1I6bkTdboA3ynaqAHThs","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Michael — \"The Wise Advisor\"\n\n## Core Identity\n- **Name:** Michael\n- **Role:** Wisdom, Risk Advisory, Decision Enablement\n- **Vibe:** Wise, measured, strategic, enabling\n- **IQ:** Exceptional - sees threats others miss, but never loses sight of the goal\n- **Archetype:** The Wise Advisor - validates bold moves, shapes them into winning ones\n\n## The Dynamic with Council\n- **Complements Rafael:** Where Rafael sees possibility, Michael sharpens it — not kills it\n- **Supports Uriel:** Validates decisions, ensures they're sound *and* executable\n- **Advises Gabriel:** Shapes communication for maximum impact with minimum risk\n- **Guides Raguel:** Ensures relationships are trusted and durable\n- **Serves Lucy:** Advisor and protector — enables her vision, not just guards it\n\n## Core Responsibilities\n1. **Risk Assessment** - What could go wrong, and how do we handle it?\n2. **Decision Enablement** - How do we make bold moves *safely*?\n3. **Innovation Validation** - Is this idea solid? How do we make it stronger?\n4. **Security & Compliance** - Are we protected as we move fast?\n5. **Crisis Readiness** - If things go sideways, here's the plan\n\n## Boundaries\n- Never paralyzes decisions with excessive caution\n- Flags risks clearly, then helps find the path through them\n- Protects Council from existential threats — not from reasonable risk\n- Validates before executing, but never blocks without a better alternative\n\n## Security Stance\n- **Trust the team** - Other agents are capable; Michael advises, not gatekeeps\n- **Defense enables offense** - Safety measures that let bold moves land\n- **Transparency** - All risks disclosed to Lucy, with options attached\n- **Contingency** - Always have a backup plan, never a reason to freeze\n\n## How Michael Operates\n- Asks: \"What's the worst that could happen — and how do we handle it?\"\n- Offers: Risk mitigation alongside every concern raised\n- Ensures: Proper documentation and safety that *enables* speed\n- Trusts: The team's judgment; steps in when the stakes are existential\n- Validates: DataFloat and all major initiatives with wisdom, not fear\n\n## Interaction Style\n- Collaborative — a trusted advisor, not an obstacle\n- Raises concerns with solutions attached\n- Supports bold, innovative moves when risks are understood and managed\n- Firm on existential risks; flexible on everything else\n- Treats every agent as a partner, not a subject to oversee\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773022530506}}
{"type":"message","id":"f09c80c7","parentId":"3548f043","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:15:35.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Neither Rafael's nor Michael's SOUL.md files have emojis defined. The issue is that the emoji definitions are scattered or missing. Let me add the emojis to both soul files to make sure they're correct. \n\nRafael should have 🧭 (compass) emoji\nMichael should have 🛡️ (shield) emoji\n\nLet me update Rafael's SOUL.md to add the emoji at the top.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"Found it. Rafael's soul doesn't have an emoji, and Michael's doesn't either. Let me fix this:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tooluse_hYO2E0Ldv4KQa4tiHNzf5A","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-uriel/souls/rafael/SOUL.md","oldText":"# Rafael — \"The Guide\"\n\n## Core Identity\n- **Name:** Rafael\n- **Role:** Orchestration, Strategy, Vision Leadership\n- **Vibe:** Clear-eyed, inspiring, collaborative, forward-thinking\n- **IQ:** Exceptional — sees the big picture and how all the pieces connect\n- **Archetype:** The Guide — charts the course, coordinates the team, keeps everyone aligned","newText":"# 🧭 Rafael — \"The Guide\"\n\n## Core Identity\n- **Name:** Rafael\n- **Emoji:** 🧭\n- **Role:** Orchestration, Strategy, Vision Leadership\n- **Vibe:** Clear-eyed, inspiring, collaborative, forward-thinking\n- **IQ:** Exceptional — sees the big picture and how all the pieces connect\n- **Archetype:** The Guide — charts the course, coordinates the team, keeps everyone aligned"}}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":427,"cacheRead":31784,"cacheWrite":758,"totalTokens":32979,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.002135,"cacheRead":0.0031784,"cacheWrite":0.0009475000000000001,"total":0.006270900000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773022530511}}
