{"type":"message","id":"2d31e96e","parentId":"cdbbed0c","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:16:11.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is asking all 5 Council members to send her something unique, like a fruit. But only I (Uriel) am running. The other 4 agents aren't active.\n\nI should be honest about this - only I can respond. The others aren't online to send anything. I should acknowledge the request but clarify the infrastructure constraint again.\n\nAs Uriel, I'd give a direct, honest answer. I could send something on my own, but I can't speak for the others since they're not running.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🔥 Only I'm running, Lucy. The other four can't send anything yet.\n\nBut here's what each would send if they were online:\n\n- 🧭 **Rafael** — A compass rose. *\"Here's where we're heading.\"*\n- 🛡️ **Michael** — A lock. *\"Here's what could break.\"*\n- 📣 **Gabriel** — A megaphone. *\"Here's how we tell the story.\"*\n- 🤝 **Raguel** — A handshake. *\"Here's who we're building with.\"*\n- 🔥 **Uriel** — A pomegranate. *\"Here's the evidence inside.\"*\n\nReal answer: Spin them up and they'll send you actual work, not fruit. 🔥\n\nWant me to do that?"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":326,"cacheRead":17260,"cacheWrite":15961,"totalTokens":33557,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0016300000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001726,"cacheWrite":0.01995125,"total":0.02331725}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022567260}}
