{"type":"message","id":"73ea67f2","parentId":"b42ce29e","timestamp":"2026-03-09T02:17:27.038Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lucy is saying that Raphael said Michael's signature is Lemons, and they think the one with lemon is having hallucinations.\n\nWait - Raphael isn't running. Only I (Uriel) am running. So Lucy is either:\n1. Testing me\n2. Confused about who's running\n3. Talking to someone else (another agent they spun up separately?)\n4. Referring to something from a conversation I wasn't part of\n\nI should clarify: Raphael hasn't said anything to me because he's not running. If someone told Lucy that Michael's signature is lemons, it wasn't Raphael through me.\n\nLet me be direct as Uriel - I need ground truth here.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🔥 Stop. Ground truth check:\n\n**Raphael isn't running.** I'm the only agent active right now. If Raphael told you something about Michael and lemons, it wasn't through me.\n\nEither:\n1. You're testing me (fair)\n2. You spun up agents separately on the VPS and they're talking to you directly\n3. Someone else is claiming to be Raphael\n\nWhich is it? 🔥"}],"api":"bedrock-converse-stream","provider":"amazon-bedrock","model":"us.anthropic.claude-haiku-4-5-20251001-v1:0","usage":{"input":10,"output":280,"cacheRead":33221,"cacheWrite":249,"totalTokens":33760,"cost":{"input":0.000009999999999999999,"output":0.0014000000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0033221,"cacheWrite":0.00031125,"total":0.00504335}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773022643129}}
